org.hibernate.type.spi

Class StandardSpiBasicTypes

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.type.spi.StandardSpiBasicTypes

  • public final class StandardSpiBasicTypes
extends Object
    Centralizes access to the standard set of basic types.

    Type mappings can be adjusted per SessionFactory (technically per TypeConfiguration.
